this_title: 行き暮れども待ち明かず
introduction: Yukie Saito's deeply disturbing Benighted but Not Begun (1994) stars the filmmaker and her boyfriend, who kicks her out of bed, shoves her out the door, forces her to walk nude through a filthy chicken hatchery, and worse. In this story of human obliteration, power and gender are one subject.
chinese_title: 行き暮れども待ち明かず
